 be good (of weather)","tags":["Classical"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ʔasˤ.ħaː/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n23843","headword_ar":"اصحى","root":"SHw","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see 1, in four places. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSoHayonaA","text_ar":"اَصْحَيْنَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We became in a case of cloudlessness"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the sky"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"day"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (Msb, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the sky became cloudless to us."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSoHayotuhu mino sukorihi","text_ar":"اَصْحَيْتُهُ مِنْ سُكْرِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I recovered him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"roused him, from his intoxication"},{"kind":"text","text":"], and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino","text_ar":"مِنْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nawomihi","text_ar":"نَوْمِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from his sleep"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  And sometimes"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iSoHaA='N","text_ar":"اـِصْحَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is used as meaning The act of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rousing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"recalling to mindfulness, from a state of heedlessness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inadvertence."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}